<paragraph id="8B8E36FEFFB2FFACFF19FCB5A608FC93" blockId="8.[189,304,828,854]" box="[189,304,828,854]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">
<heading id="D0C68192FFB2FFACFF19FCB5A608FC93" bold="true" box="[189,304,828,854]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="8" pageNumber="156" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B945EAECFFB2FFACFF19FCB5A608FC93" bold="true" box="[189,304,828,854]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8E36FEFFB2FFACFF19FCE2A27DFC2A" blockId="8.[188,1399,875,1007]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">
This species was originally described from 
<collectingCountry id="F326766EFFB2FFACFD11FCE2A5DCFC40" box="[693,740,875,901]" name="Iran" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Iran</collectingCountry>
and later discovered in 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F81CFFB2FFACFC5DFCE2A342FC40" box="[1017,1146,875,901]" country="Turkey" name="Diyarbakir" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Diyarbakır</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F81CFFB2FFACFB20FCE2A3F7FC40" box="[1156,1231,875,901]" country="Turkey" name="Elazig" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Elazığ</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F81CFFB2FFACFAA2FCE2A261FC40" box="[1286,1369,875,901]" country="Turkey" name="Mersin" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Mersin</collectingRegion>
in 
<collectingCountry id="F326766EFFB2FFACFF19FC07A629FC6D" box="[189,273,910,936]" name="Turkey" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Turkey</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B0FFFB2FFACFEBBFC07A6D0FC6D" author="Linnavuori R. E." box="[287,488,910,936]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156" pagination="369 - 414" refId="ref5274" refString="Linnavuori R. E. 2010. Studies on the Miridae (Phylinae, addenda to Deraeocorinae and Orthotylinae) of Khuzestan and the adjacent provinces of Iran (Hemiptera: Heteroptera). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae 50 (2): 369 - 414." type="journal article" year="2010">Linnavuori 2010</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B0FFFB2FFACFE50FC07A5EBFC6D" author="Matocq A. &amp; Pluot-Sigwalt D. &amp; Ozgen I." box="[500,723,910,936]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156" pagination="884 - 930" refId="ref5380" refString="Matocq A., Pluot-Sigwalt D. &amp; Ozgen I. 2014. Terrestrial Hemiptera (Heteroptera) Collected in South- East Anatolia (Diyarbakir, Mardin And Elazig Provinces) (Turkey): Second List. Munis Entomology &amp; Zoology 9 (2): 884 - 930." type="journal article" year="2014">
Matocq 
<emphasis id="B945EAECFFB2FFACFDF7FC06A5B6FC6D" box="[595,654,910,936]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">et al.</emphasis>
2014
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B0FFFB2FFACFD7BFC07A32CFC6D" author="Carapezza A. &amp; Kment P." box="[735,1044,910,936]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156" pagination="253" refId="ref4869" refString="Carapezza A. &amp; Kment P. 2018. Psallus thomashenryi sp. nov. and Psallus lucanicus from Turkey (Hemiptera, Heteroptera, Miridae). ZooKeys 796: 253. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / ZOOKEYS. 796.21536" type="journal article" year="2018">Carapezza &amp; Kment 2018</bibRefCitation>
). It is characterized by whitish yellow coloration, pale yellow vestiture, immaculate tibiae and lack of black dot below membranal cells (
<figureCitation id="130A2A7BFFB2FFACFF61FC5DA627FC2B" box="[197,287,980,1006]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="7.[189,232,1928,1954]" captionTargetBox="[305,1266,368,1872]" captionTargetId="figure-16@7.[305,1283,362,1892]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Fig. 4. Plagiognathus spp. A. P. ozgurkocaki sp. nov., ♂, paratype (LEMT). B. P. marivanensis Linnavuori, 2010, ♂ (BCIT), Karaman. C. P. bipunctatus albicans (Reuter, 1901), ♂ (BCIT), Karaman. D. P. bipunctatus bipunctatus, ♂ (BCIT), İzmir. Scale bar = 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6402847" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6402847/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Fig. 4B</figureCitation>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B0FFFB2FFACFE93FC5DA53AFC2B" author="Linnavuori R. E." box="[311,514,980,1006]" pageId="8" pageNumber="156" pagination="369 - 414" refId="ref5274" refString="Linnavuori R. E. 2010. Studies on the Miridae (Phylinae, addenda to Deraeocorinae and Orthotylinae) of Khuzestan and the adjacent provinces of Iran (Hemiptera: Heteroptera). Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae 50 (2): 369 - 414." type="journal article" year="2010">Linnavuori 2010</bibRefCitation>
). This species is recorded from 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F81CFFB2FFACFCD2FC5CA4DAFC2A" box="[886,994,981,1007]" country="Turkey" name="Karaman" pageId="8" pageNumber="156">Karaman</collectingRegion>
for the first time in this paper.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
